Structure of the mall is little unique compare to remaining malls because box office is available on other side of the mall just makes people confuse
Look of the mall is fabulous
This mall is very near to railway station
Parking is also congested
Even u can find ev charging station over here

Recently saw Pushpa 2 reloaded version Jan 21st  2025 and there was no Ac working ..There were No staff member to be seen at all … no food was kept at the interval …and no body was there at the food counter.The  staff member later was seen at the Ross omlet shop working there as part time … The Quality of this place is gone down completely because of unprofessional staff members and no cleanliness maintained and No security at all as anyone was entering to use the toilet as a public toilet.This could lead  to criminal activities in the future.I am from Vasco and I want this place to improve.. please hire staff who is willing to work professionally and maintain this place.

It's small and very cosy, like your personal sitting room, seats are super comfy especially at LUXE where you get nice recliner. screens are small so dnt book your seats far from screen. Ac was very chilling. They could improve on their eating menu though which doesn't have much to choose from

description:
**Restaurant Review: 1930 Vasco in Goa**

With an overall rating of 4.1 from a substantial 1,435 reviews, 1930 Vasco stands out as a flourishing establishment in the bustling landscape of Goa. Patrons frequently mention essentials such as "recliner" seating (40 counts), well-placed "screens" (33 counts), and the convenience of "parking" options (15 counts), showcasing its appeal as an ideal spot for a cozy meal or a relaxing cinema experience.

**Ambiance & Design**

Upon stepping into 1930 Vasco, guests are greeted by a unique and fabulous ambiance. The mall structure offers a cozy, intimate feel reminiscent of a personal sitting room; the seating arrangements are adorned with plush recliners that invite you to unwind. Notably, the images encapsulate the mall's modern flair alongside comfy decor, marking it as a commuter-friendly destination near the railway station, though parking can be a bit congested at busier times. The attention to detail in the design has created a warm atmosphere, perfect for a casual catch-up or a chill-out session before a movie.

**Menu & Culinary Experience**

The culinary offerings, however, seem to be a point of contention among diners. While the drinks and snacks are served in a casual format, many reviews indicate the menu could benefit from a broader selection. A cozy yet limited menu, particularly noted during busy hours, may leave some guests desiring more formal culinary options. Patrons hinted at a need for diversity, especially when visitors are keen on enjoying a meal before or after a movie. 

**Customer Experience & Service**

Customer service experiences vary significantly, with some reviews detailing a lack of staff presence at critical times, particularly at food counters. Complaints have surfaced regarding cleanliness and unprofessional service, suggesting a need for a dedicated effort to improve staff efficiency and maintain the place’s overall hygiene. The relaxed vibe is further dampened by reports of malfunctioning air conditioning during peak times, a notable downside for guests expecting comfort and convenience.

**Popularity & Reviews**

Despite mixed feedback, 1930 Vasco remains a popular choice for local residents and moviegoers alike. Its charm resonates on social media, where patrons highlight the cozy seating and ambiance. However, the establishment may want to consider some structural changes and staff training to elevate customer satisfaction further. By addressing these concerns, 1930 Vasco could enhance its reputation and turn occasional visitors into regulars.

**Visual Highlights**

The customer-provided images reinforce the restaurant's charm, showcasing the inviting seating areas that underscore comfort with a modern touch. The vibrant atmosphere paired with aesthetically pleasing design elements makes for great visual appeal, inviting diners to sit back and enjoy their surroundings while awaiting their meals or the next screening.

**Conclusion**

In summary, 1930 Vasco offers a blend of comfort and casual dining that appeals to a diverse crowd. While it shines with its cozy ambiance and comfortable seating, there are elements in service and menu variety that need to be addressed for the restaurant to reach its full potential. With a few enhancements, 1930 Vasco can solidify its position as a preferred spot for both gastronomy and entertainment in Goa.
